2007-07-29  Chris Toshok  <toshok@ximian.com>

	* collection.h, collection.cpp: change "ResourceCollection" to
	"ResourceDictionary".

	* uielement.cpp: same.

	* type.cpp, type.h, value.cpp, value.h: same.

