	Silverlight docs).

2007-06-22  Jeffrey Stedfast  <fejj@novell.com>

	* xaml.cpp (matrix_value_from_str): use delete[] to free the array
	of doubles instead of g_free() as it was allocated with new, not
	g_malloc().

